Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:07.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\shad1\4c&HF7F4F2&\pos(100,360)}回\N鍋\N肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會做這種了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 厲害 這不是回鍋肉麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓壞了 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放了幾味秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能嘗出來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有秘方 做得很認真嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說只有醬的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是秘方放得太秘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說這幾味秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越嚼越覺得相當難吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矛盾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs36\frz10.565\b0\pos(753,421)\c&H7E7C7F&}河童\N很有型吧☆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在畫河童…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 很有型吧什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次畫的東西幻想色彩強點的話可能會更有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大巨人和河童 什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs33}デイダラボッチ：神奈川縣一個傳說中的巨人，他用籐條把富士山綁在後背旅行；\N還有傳說是他將羽黑山（櫪木縣）掛在腰間在鬼怒河洗腳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 是受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童 河童吶 河童
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童（KAPPA） PA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PA PA 寄生蟲（Parasite）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按著這個發展 來玩畫畫接詞遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PA RA SI TE？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：小祐以日文羅馬音的方式念那個英文單詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PARASITE是這樣的生物啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這個箭頭的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是要邀我玩畫畫接詞遊戲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就接受你的邀請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 PARASITE啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TE TE 誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz16.388\c&H6D6C6E&\pos(690,190)}沒時間了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且畫個天狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PA RA SA I TO的TO讀作TE了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：Parasite作為英文單詞的日式念法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗（TEN GU）GU GU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GU GU！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TENGO！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TENGO是啥玩意啊 TENGO！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生應該不會犯這麼幼稚而拙劣的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 把天狗畫出來了 又特意用文字標注一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是勉強用GO來接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs39\c&H7E7C7F&\frz20.131\pos(674,573)}悟空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H7E7C7F&\frz20.131\pos(890,440)}畫小點!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個厭倦的悟空是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？悟空（GO KUU）？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我花的應該是天狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 腦袋裡想著GU 但是變成GO了這種事我也能理解呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來之後可以問她要果汁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來 是U哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U U 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓜（U RI）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 兔子（U SA GI）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H7E7C7F&\frz355.12\pos(657,270)}畫不好啊～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛啊！（U SI）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這頭牛太過分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌頭（SHI TA）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫了個舌頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 是TA哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TA TA 出租車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：日式讀音是TA KU SIー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為 為毛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來可不是TAXI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是TA KU SU Iー啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 隨便畫畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\c&H7E7C7F&\frz31.202\pos(578,500)}司壽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：年輕人喜歡把詞語反過來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用業界術語哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我可幹勁十足啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 這樣不是輸了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:55.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\c&H7E7C7F&\frz19.26\pos(767,613)}SUPERMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：接詞遊戲最後一個音是N的話就輸了，因為日語沒有以N開頭的詞彙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\frz19.26\c&H212022&\pos(451,546)}SUPERMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 等等 這裡這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\c&H7E7C7F&\frz19.26\pos(837,601)}SUPERMANS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:18.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\fad(520,520)\shad1\pos(1100,360)\4c&HFFFFFF&\b0}圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊啊 關口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 關口 來玩划拳吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}日式划拳：決定先手，三人以上的話決定順時針或逆時針進行；每個人手握拳；喊「一起來」\N然後喊一個數字，範圍是0到所有玩家的大拇指的數量，同時所有玩家立起來任意數量的拇指；\N如果立起來的拇指合起來跟喊的數字一樣，喊的人就放下一隻手，放下的手不參加遊戲；\N下一個玩家開始。如此反覆，首先兩隻手都放下的玩家贏得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關口～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這麼無聊 偶爾也陪我玩一下嘛～～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關口…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：俳句
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罰站最上川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近來忘記作業了就要上走廊罰站真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫漫一堂課
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎度最上川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同 同學們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿 鹿！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼校長要把鹿…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我說… 校長… 鹿 鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我說 同學們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀕死啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹿煎餅！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：日本動物園裡能買到的專門喂鹿的小餅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我說 同學們 校長他 要死… 要死…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬上去啦——！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛起來啦——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那麼摔下去了——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又爬上去了——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下來了——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無 無計可施啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長——！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 大家 DEATH 校長 DEATH…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站 站——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…那個 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 大家 聽我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊裡沒有任何異常情況！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是心底裡最真實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是想要袒護校長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得說明太麻煩了之類的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向剛才上演一場殊死搏鬥的勇者們表達敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊集五月雨 奔騰最上川
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：松尾芭蕉的俳句
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意義不明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:09.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\shad1\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1190,360)}10\N元\N足\N球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那～麼～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒是裁判哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10元足球不是不需要裁判麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂啊 這種東西是心境哦心境！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪裡都可以 儘管放馬過來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭 接下來是布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石剪布可不帶喲 石頭剪子布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喀嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗嘿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：韓語的我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住一隻 蟑螂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要慎重…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要慎重而行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓這令人作嘔的惡的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再一次在這個家中蔓延…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想個 得想個最好的計策…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺蟲噴霧劑…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能一擊必殺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能被它逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想看到它翻滾掙扎的樣子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 洗滌劑呢！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在茶几上塗滿洗滌劑的話就能封住他的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後用針尖瞄準這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在飛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無處可逃的話這傢伙一定會飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會朝著人胡亂飛過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是 這東西鑽到身體裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！！停在臉上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我說 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是 進… 進到嘴裡面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西要是進嘴裡面了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下就ROCK and ROLL了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的恐懼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有解決辦法！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個碗開啟的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選項就只有死亡或者去死這兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEATH or DIE！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\shad0\bord0\c&H2C2F2E&\frz5.892\pos(610,376)}垃圾\N垃圾\N垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能那樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪 阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這裡面有隻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑… 蟑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 是蟑螂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會抓住的 你把碗開啟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把碗舉起來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話不是抓不到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在說什麼啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在封印著惡的化身！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是潘多拉之盒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開啟的那一瞬就是DEATH or DIE啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不開啟碗的話我怎麼抓它啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請自己開啟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個毛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼辦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生也不知道去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的點心是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好時機！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士反正也不怕蟲子 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 這 這個碗裡面的蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處 處理一下的話就幫大忙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RO RO RO ROCK and ROLL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思 那拜託了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:16:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一下子拍死哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼煩惱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人… 這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士什麼的最討厭了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼噠 騙你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能討厭博士呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 我最喜歡你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 博士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 我們開始ROCK and ROLL了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:09.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\shad1\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(100,360)}數\N到\N10\N的\N話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱哦 我可以出去麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？不是才剛進來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 到10的話就出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說到10的話就可以出去了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得這麼數哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:41.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\fad(520,520)\shad1\pos(1160,360)\4c&HFFFFFF&\b0}圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說要去補課 所以都回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關口也是 好無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來關口你不去補課麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐 咖哩怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經非常餓了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也超餓的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 你那邊怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺要來條大的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來能大快朵頤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經感覺很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 久等了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超美味的超級咖哩 完成之章哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊還得花點時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做咖哩前放裡邊就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 小寶寶哭之前不要開啟蓋子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}譯註：日本流傳的做飯口訣「始めちょろちょろ、中ぱっぱ、赤子泣くとも蓋取るな」 直譯\N是開始涓涓，中間啪啪，寶寶哭了，蓋也別拿；意指一開始火弱，中間火強，途中不要開啟蓋子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要是把蛋黃醬也帶來的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩就要配蛋黃醬哪 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋… 蛋黃… 蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子喜歡搭配什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是…不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有涼粉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼…粉… 什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美 美緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的血是什麼色的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯的咖哩和米飯都沒了！
