Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這個給大家輪流吃
